ETS VS ARIMA MEDIANTE CROSS VALIDATION

fets <- function(x, h) {
  forecast(ets(x), h = h)
}
farima <- function(x, h) {
  forecast(auto.arima(x), h = h)
}

e1 <- tsCV(IPI$general, fets, h = 1)
e2 <- tsCV(IPI$general, farima, h = 1)

MSE_ets<-mean(e1^2, na.rm = TRUE) 
MSR_AR<-mean(e2^2, na.rm = TRUE)
